txt.en: 'Retreat my brethren, the dark tide of Angmar spreads!'
'Our last stand is now! Bring them down! Bring them down!'
'Angmar has grown daft! Why would I leave the safety of this tower. No, no; face me here or not at all!'
'To arms, to arms, do not let this fight slip through our grasp!'
'Stand true and smash this upstart war host!'
'We shall drive back this force from the North. Come Men, let us show this war host our strength!'
